1 AN ACT
2 To amend and reenact R.S. 17:3351(A)(2), relative to postsecondary education management
3 boards; to provide the use of and conditions on all amounts received by public
4 postsecondary education institutions from the Board of Regents Support Fund; to
5 require public postsecondary education management boards to continue to comply
